2. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper discusses a communication framework involving wireless radio equipment and multiple receivers, which falls under the domain of networking and internet architecture. 
3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper deals with designing a communication system that ensures quality of service guarantees, which is a problem in systems and control. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper discusses the transmission of data alongside power, which could potentially involve multimedia data. 
5. cs.AR (Hardware Architecture) - The paper involves designing receiver structures for energy harvesting, which could potentially involve hardware architecture.
